The TDD exercise is complete. All 9 tests pass and `experiment-done.txt` has been written.

**Summary of what was implemented:**

- `src/game-of-life.spec.ts` — 9 tests covering all Game of Life rules
- `src/game-of-life.ts` — Implementation with:
  - `nextGeneration(cells)` — computes survivors + born cells
  - `neighborsOf(cell)` — Moore neighborhood (single source of truth for adjacency)
  - `countNeighbors(cells, cell)` — counts live neighbors using `neighborsOf`
